FBIS4-3552 "drchi078_d_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 Northeast Asia XINHUA Notes Defense Secretary Perry's Arrival in Japan XINHUA Notes Defense Secretary Perry's Arrival in Japan OW2104130594 Beijing XINHUA in English 1242 GMT 21 Apr 94 OW2104130594 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Tokyo, April 21 (XINHUA) -- U.S. Defense Secretary William Perry arrived in Tokyo today from Seoul for a two-day visit to Japan for talks with Japanese Government leaders. Perry will meet with Japanese Defense Agency Director General Kazuo Aichi this evening and Foreign Minister Tsutomu Hata tomorrow, Japanese officials said. He is expected to discuss with the Japanese leaders policy coordination to deal with possible hostilities as concern deepens over Pyongyang's refusal to allow full international inspections of it nuclear facilities.
